# IDE / project files (regenerated by Unity)
*.csproj
# …but the headless test harness project is hand-authored and CI needs it:
!Tools/EngineVerify/*.csproj
# …and so is the SoI mass-sim console (CI checks it out but never builds the exe):
!Tools/SoiSim/*.csproj
*.sln
*.slnx
*.suo
